TI  - Enhancing Business Continuity in the Oil and Gas Industry through Electronic Records Management System Usage to Improve Off-Site Working: A Narrative Review
PY  - 2022
T2  - Journal of Information Science Theory and Practice
VL  - 10
IS  - 2
